title: Lynda - InDesign 2014 Creative Cloud Updates with Justin Seeley
description:
Lynda - InDesign 2014 Creative Cloud Updates with Justin Seeley 
42m 8s Intermediate Jun 18, 2014 Updated Oct 06, 2014 | Uploaded in Nov 8, 2014 by 2boweb

Subjects:    Design, Page Layout 
Software:    InDesign 



Creative Cloud puts the latest Adobe technology at your fingertips, which means programs like InDesign CC change frequently. Justin Seeley helps you stay on top of all these updates and get the most out of InDesign's newest features and enhancements. New chapters will be added every time Adobe releases a major update. To start, Justin reviews color groups, the enhanced packaging workflow, drag-and-drop table functionality, and Behance integration. Check back often for new tutorials
